### 订单服务 Sentinel 熔断降级测试

### 1. 订单查询测试 (带Sentinel保护)
GET http://localhost:8000/order/123
Accept: application/json

### 2. 订单创建测试 (有随机异常，测试熔断)
POST http://localhost:8000/order/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1001,
  "quantity": 2,
  "price": 99.99,
  "userId": 1
}

### 3. 订单状态更新测试 (有随机异常，测试降级)
PUT http://localhost:8000/order/456/status?status=shipped
Accept: application/json

### 4. 连续多次请求测试 - 触发熔断
GET http://localhost:8000/order/789

### 5. 无效参数测试 - 触发异常降级
GET http://localhost:8000/order/0

### 6. 空订单创建测试 - 触发异常降级
POST http://localhost:8000/order/create
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 7. 无效状态更新测试
PUT http://localhost:8000/order/123/status?status=
Accept: application/json
